119
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,520
We don't live far.

120
00:09:43,719 --> 00:09:45,479
Okay. Sign here and go back.

121
00:09:51,638 --> 00:09:53,067
(Student's signature: Zhuo Yifeng
Family member's signature)

122
00:10:00,359 --> 00:10:01,039
