205
00:15:37,599 --> 00:15:38,599
I added some celery.

206
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:41,159
It is pretty conducive
to cardiovascular system.

207
00:15:41,479 --> 00:15:42,479
Drink it up.

208
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,159
I'll get the door.

209
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,159
You...

210
