218
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,119
is overcooked.

219
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,719
The salad

220
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,479
isn't fresh.

221
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:10,760
The bitter gourd and honey juice

222
